name: Booma
Lore: 'Lunched from fanbaa-mounted catapults. Gungan ''energy balls'' are used to disable a variety of mechanized threats. Effectiveness is enhanced by the skill of the user.',
Text: 'Deploy on your Fambaa. Twice during battle may draw destiny. If destiny < total number of opponent''s characters and vehicles present, one of them is lost (opponent''s choice).',
